name: MEV Capital M^0 Morpho Vault
description: The MEV Capital M^0 vault curated by MEV Capital is dedicated to providing capital to M^0 protocol markets. It offers borrowers access to attractive rates through M^0 incentives and provides suppliers with a competitive APR. Morpho Vaults are curated lending vaults that can allocate deposits to any number of Morpho Markets. Each vault is customizable and has a different risk profile. Curators are independent, third-party risk experts who use their expertise to offer various Morpho Vaults.
